@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1 style="text-align:center">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p><b>Last updated:</b> 08.30.2025</p>

<h3>Welcome to [Your Site Name] (“we”, “our”, “us”). We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our website and services.</h3>

<h5>1. Information We Collect</h5>
<p><b>We may collect the following types of information:</b></p>
<ol>
    <li><b>Personal Information:</b> Name, email address, phone number, and any details you provide when creating an account or applying for a job.</li>
    <li><b>Professional Information:</b> Resume, work experience, skills, and other data shared in job applications.</li>
    <li><b>Technical Information:</b> IP address, browser type, device information, and usage data collected through cookies and similar technologies.</li>
</ol>

<h5>2. How We Use Your Information</h5>
<ul>
    <li>Provide and improve our services.</li>
    <li>Match job seekers with potential employers.</li>
    <li>Send notifications, updates, and promotional offers (only if you opt in).</li>
    <li>Ensure the security and functionality of our website.</li>
</ul>

<h5>3. How We Share Your Information</h5>
<p>We may share your information:</p>
<ul>
    <li>With employers when you apply for a job.</li>
    <li>With service providers that help us operate our platform.</li>
    <li>When required by law or to protect our legal rights.</li>
</ul>
<p><b>We never sell your personal data to third parties.</b></p>

<h5>4. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h5>
<p>We use cookies to enhance your browsing experience, analyze traffic, and provide personalized content. You can manage your cookie preferences in your browser settings.</p>

<h5>5. Data Retention</h5>
<p>We retain your information as long as necessary to provide services or comply with legal obligations. You can request deletion of your account at any time.</p>

<h5>6. Your Rights</h5>
<ul>
    <li>Access, update, or delete your personal information.</li>
    <li>Withdraw consent for data processing.</li>
    <li>Contact us for any privacy-related concerns.</li>
</ul>

<h5>7. Security</h5>
<p>We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your data, but please note that no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.</p>

<h5>8. Contact Us</h5>
<p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
<p><b>Email:</b> support@yoursite.com</p>
